{"tid":865220,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有無天主教預言拎？傾下花地瑪、宗座預言。","createTime":"2018-10-17T00:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T11:49:47.000Z","uid":164871,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"44ee712bab80b6d37cca8967fc31b5273601cdd8","tid":865220,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:51:49.000Z","msg":"花地瑪預言︰<br />\n<br />\n帳面公開有三個﹐預言在地獄情況、蘇共成立和解體、教宗JP II 遇刺。但有隱藏版話兩個聖人一個教宗後教會會解體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/法蒂瑪的三個秘密\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E6%B3%95%E8%92%82%E7%91%AA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86&d=UvGwKXXtoiGJJSbm9hgHqG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8e0ebe17\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/法蒂瑪的三個秘密</a><br />\n<br />\n宗座預言︰<br />\n<br />\n基本上就係有人條見到異象﹐佢見曬未來所有教宗﹐所以就寫左個預言出黎。<br />\n有趣既係﹐佢個預言一直都中到十足十。而係預言中﹐依個教宗就係最後一個。跟住教會玩完。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/教宗預言\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80&d=UvGwKXXtoiGJJSbm9hgHqG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=dda985cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/教宗預言</a><br />\n<br />\n依個教宗咁親中國﹐考慮埋啟示錄既大紅龍（有人理解成共產中國）﹐真係係好應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c114a711dacbbf60b389cb5f08c8f5781be64e2","tid":865220,"uid":22535,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"44ee712bab80b6d37cca8967fc31b5273601cdd8","tid":865220,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:51:49.000Z","msg":"花地瑪預言︰<br />\n<br />\n帳面公開有三個﹐預言在地獄情況、蘇共成立和解體、教宗JP II 遇刺。但有隱藏版話兩個聖人一個教宗後教會會解體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/法蒂瑪的三個秘密\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E6%B3%95%E8%92%82%E7%91%AA%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86&d=UvGwKXXtoiGJJSbm9hgHqG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D